body:
I cannot replicate the problem (I am on Sierra)

Try doing the following from the tensorflow root directory (make sure everything else was compiled :

``` bash
brew install automake autoconf libtool
tensorflow/contrib/makefile/build_all_ios.sh
```

If that works, the documentation has to updated, if it doesn't, what is the error that fails? Note that the process might take some time to finish.
